➜被萌到失控，人类这种变态生理反应，其实是你活下去的救星
http://www.sohu.com/a/420310675_624188	24205
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/84ba1bf12d7d43ca9e002000a16e1e15.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每当看到可爱的东西时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类总是控制不住自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们一开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能只是单纯地<strong>摸一摸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/d6d81e04174d4b2580592002b9815ff1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摸着摸着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不自主地开始<strong>捏一捏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200923/66a17f76cc5e4ff298d1de797ec109e3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就演变成了——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/96594e8571d74402adfc9bd0adf2950d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手法是一步比一步狂暴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">内心也是一步比一步<strong>“变态”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至萌发出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“好可爱啊，真想一屁股坐死它”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的想法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当回过神来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往往会陷入沉思</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“完了完了，我不会是变态吧”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“我不会是有虐待倾向吧”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“不会只有我一个人这样吧”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200923/3a91f235a7c349bf970bcfaf3030030e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2015年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耶鲁大学就做过一项研究</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实验招募了109位志愿者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给他们观看<strong>可爱动物/婴儿</strong>的照片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让志愿者来描述自己的感受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和你一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不少人在被萌到的同时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有种马上要<strong>“失控”</strong>的感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会产生想<strong>狠狠地捏一把</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咬一口或锤一拳</strong>的念头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人甚至会像发现<strong>可口猎物</strong>一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发出可怕的声音</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1c908b7a81884bb78ea7afe08e058e48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了验证这些人是说说而已</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是真的会付诸行动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在第二阶段的测试中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">研究员给志愿者发了<strong>气泡纸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">激动的时候可以捏气泡发泄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在观看<strong>搞笑或者正常短片</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捏爆的泡泡数目有80-100个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在观看<strong>萌宠婴儿</strong>时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捏爆的泡泡数目有120个泡泡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1325b0a3be16446cab4288befc49fd0b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很明显</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被萌到后确实有那种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是虐待，但就是控制不住自己手的感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而他们为这种欲望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起了个非常中二的名字叫——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萌系侵略性现象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/7843881460af42ecb910494a2e1de74f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/cd322dec7bdd40a09660827cf35afda1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么是什么导致了我们</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>明明被萌到很喜欢</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>却又有想狠狠蹂躏一下的冲动呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加利福尼亚大学的心理医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了研究这背后的原因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">招募了54个志愿者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这次就很先进了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们使用了<strong>传感器</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来观测参与者在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到萌系图片时的脑内活动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e47e0fc2b5ba43c6b842fbf6ffe35130.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当大家在看到萌的东西时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑的奖励系统非常活跃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中脑腹侧被盖区活动增加</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简单来说就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会大量分泌<strong>多巴胺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你感觉非常快乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/dbe99a53eccb42689c42124911861bf1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多巴胺一直这么分泌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快乐是真的快乐了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但大脑一直处于这样的环境下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就像电脑一直过载操作可能<strong>蓝屏/死机</strong>一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也可能因为一直兴奋而晕厥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萌死了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要是人看一次萌物就晕一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那进化过程中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能出现两种情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200923/454ff19e4a13492988c5b790a11f3e58.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>接受</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那人类可能会灭绝吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟兔兔那么可爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到都晕了不能吃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老虎大象狮子虽然不可爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但打不过也吃不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等待你的不是只有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/39e520e433ab43e989801b622bcc0186.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/5db919e2974a4c859b463903097f7d02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不接受</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就从<strong>根源</strong>做起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接让人类对可爱无感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然就不会因可爱而晕倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吃兔兔打猪猪再也不手下留情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能够好好地进化了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/d69e98c47eb94298a09d7abf7ec90224.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在研究中发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类对可爱的这份感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也引发了人类强烈的<strong>照顾欲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我们来试想一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本来婴儿哭泣的情况会是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e7c60c797cb547468fee985e4a0a8b19.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当你丧失了对可爱的感觉后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那可能只剩下——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/af80835e6e9942baa629be3c105feb6f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就光靠一腔责任感来支撑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你养孩子期间将要面对的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>屎屁尿以及哭叫吵闹</strong>等各种问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能不当场把孩子丢了的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那真的是很强了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更多的孩子可能面对的是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/c67fcd10b68145ebb44c729afc7bfbe0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很明显</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上面两条路对人类繁衍进化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都有一定的<strong>阻碍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有萌感不行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丢了也不行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只能让脑子出来干事了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/bd67e796a411455db7a0276abd539769.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想克制消极情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能有<strong>可乐炸鸡薯条游戏</strong>......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一堆辅助快乐的东西在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/074248aebd3447618bdf3fca9e0a5722.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想快速克制积极情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就还真<strong>挺难的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟这种在兴头上的事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎么能说停就停</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑只好来一剂<strong>勐药</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把你拉回现实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/20b28c64ef4a46c3baa5d94d90572009.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没错</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是通过这些仿佛变态般的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>捏、揉、打</strong>这类消极表达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来宣泄一下你要满溢出来的情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面对有生命的物体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类通常不会真的暴揍一顿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是通过<strong>捏脸、狂亲</strong>的方式来宣泄一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而对于<strong>无生命的物体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200923/af9634492d64412987dc8e2d459d4c98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到萌物时的失控行为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阿伟的无数次惨死背后的真相</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是<strong>大脑为了防止你被萌死</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>做出努力</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而像这种萌到深处想暴揍的反应</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实在生活中还有很多别的表现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被统称为<strong>情绪二态表达</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/13afba190985456e806520fa0bfe2651.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情绪二态表达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是两种完全相反的情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同时表现了出现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>高兴得哭出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>愤怒到笑出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/487640944f6e496c94a990fba834c079.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这全都是<strong>大脑的小妙招</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为无论是积极情绪还是消极情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>高强度的反应</strong>下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都会给身体带来一定的<strong>负面影响</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了尽快制止你沉迷其中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑就会让<strong>完全相反的情绪对冲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以看到别人哭着哭着就笑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑着笑着又哭了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不一定证明他是<strong>神经病</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——有可能只是他的脑子在努力为他续命</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1f5dcd3963244ce19d3973aab43d13ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而我们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也可以把这样的情绪表达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">合理的运用在生活中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下次再遇到女朋友问你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/653573c214a54465a61e56d96c7a1087.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想赞扬她超级无敌巨可爱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却找不到哪个词合适的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你这样回答——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/f25b9b15cd944fb8b07321bcdc7338c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">温柔美丽的她们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一定会开心地笑出来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/03c07a07db124a4c937317042c74f484.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如果你被揍了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那肯定是因为——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/645733aa1bbe4f8b89cabb14fa7fc35b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
